tandard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-ablution-wudu","tag-children-al-awlad","tag-community-jamaah","tag-daughters-al-banat","tag-ease-al-yusr","tag-gentleness-al-rifq","tag-kindness-al-latf","tag-manners-adab","tag-moderation-wasitiyyah","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-women-al-nisa","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-27l","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34431,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/04\/allah-forgives-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Allah and His creatures forgive callers to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah forgives the callers to prayer when they end their call, and every creature on land or sea who hears his voice seeks forgiveness for him.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6202 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/salah-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet stresses the greatness of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he asked him about the best of deeds. The Prophet said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen prayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8150,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/fifty-salat-five-a-day\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Fifty prayers reduces to five prayers a day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Allah commanded your Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to perform fifty prayers in a day. Then, the Prophet asked his Lord Almighty about it, so Allah made them five prayers in a day. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2885 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/rinse-nose-mouth-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Rinsing the nose and mouth in ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ghatafan reported: I entered the home of Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and I found him performing ablution. Then, I saw him rinsing his nose and mouth, and he said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would do so two or three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/prophet-siwak-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: The Prophet uses the toothstick often","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI was ordered to use the toothstick so often that I thought something of it would be sent down to me in the Quran or revealed to me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2998 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/16\/prophet-frees-slaves-taif\/","url_meta":{"origin":8143,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees the slaves of al-Ta&#8217;if","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, besieged the people of Al-Ta\u2019if, he freed their slaves who came out to him. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 3257 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0